<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>角色档案</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f6fb;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .card {
            width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .left {
            width: 50%;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }

        .right {
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .right img {
            width: 300px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .info {
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <div class="left">
        <h1>小九</h1>
        <div class="info">
            <p><span class="title">年龄：</span>13</p>
            <p><span class="title">身高：</span>155cm</p>
            <p><span class="title">来自：</span>原·梦林 → 现·电玩城区域</p>
            <p><span class="title">生日：</span>5月16日</p>
            <p><span class="title">种族：</span>狐</p>
            <p><span class="title">性别：</span>女</p>
            <p><span class="title">外貌特征：</span><br>
            长发，略显凌乱
有狐耳 
一只眼睛受伤，所以带上了眼罩
表情常年平淡或迟钝
身形偏瘦小，看起来很弱
行动时有一点“延迟感”（像慢半拍）
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
        <img src="character.png" alt="角色立绘">
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
